class_notes: Directed study with a Biology professor.  Permission of instructor is required.  Once permission is received, contact Tonya Woolcock at tdavis6@emory.edu to request a permission number.  This course does NOT count toward the Biology major.
course_description: Credit, one to four hours per semester. Prerequisite: permission of instructor.
prerequisites: (BIOL 142 and BIOL 142L) or BIOL_OX 142 or equivalent transfer credit as a prerequisite.
